strings: <voice_0x01000D0A><se_low>King of tricks: Ladies, you are right on at least one point! No one blinks here!
<voice_0x01000D0B><se_low>King of tricks: Well...the bar is waiting for you! We're going to go one step further. I don't want to trouble you
<voice_0x01000D0C><se_low>King of tricks: Find the brain of your friend. We are looking forward to your response!
<voice_0x01000D0D><se_low>January: Drink as much as you want! You're welcome boss! Forget about going to the brain section.
<voice_0x01000D0E><se_low>January: There are people who need to focus on their work. You need to find one dollar bill.
